      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CANYA FLAVOUR (3) rocketed out of the inside draw with a strong early sectional and gave a sight but had to settle for a placing, finishing second (30.18) at Q Parklands over 520m. Good form should continue. ZABDON COSMO (4) goes very well this course and distance starting 12 times for four wins and four minors. Missed the frame latest (22.38) when sixth over 390m at Q Lakeside in a Grade 5. Looks well placed here and among the chances. UNDENIABLE GRIT (2) produced a modest effort most recently when fifth at Grafton over 450m behind Brown Bread (26.01) in a Grade 5. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. Can figure in the finish. ZABDON CREAM BUN (1) was unplaced here last start but gets her chance to atone.",
